Token.Abstract: Protocol for handling callbacks from SFUserAccountManager.
Called before the user account manager switches from one user to another.

Parameter.Name: userAccountManager
Parameter.Abstract: The SFUserAccountManager instance making the switch.

Parameter.Name: fromUser
Parameter.Abstract: The user being switched away from.

Parameter.Name: toUser
Parameter.Abstract: The user to be switched to. nil if the user context is being switched back to no user.

Token.Abstract: Called after the user account manager switches from one user to another.

Parameter.Name: userAccountManager
Parameter.Abstract: The SFUserAccountManager instance making the switch.

Parameter.Name: fromUser
Parameter.Abstract: The user that was switched away from.

Parameter.Name: toUser
Parameter.Abstract: The user that was switched to. nil if the user context is being switched back to no user.
